# Examples:
#   "0 5,14,20 * * *"  → 5 AM, 2 PM, 8 PM IST (production)
#   "*/2 * * * *"      → every 2 minutes (testing)
#   "30 16 * * *"      → 4:30 PM IST (one-off test)
